{3000}{}{I woke up a little worse for wear this mornin'. Forgot my damn rifle, and I can't leave my post. I need you to head to my place down on the south side of town and get it for me. It'll be in a footlocker. Don't worry, it ain't locked.}
{3010}{}{No problem. Back in a second.}
{3020}{}{What's in it for me?}
{3030}{}{I don't think I can help you with that. Bye.}
{4000}{}{Well ain't you all business? Should've expected it by now. Alright you shyster, there's a couple clips of ammo you're welcome to.}
{4010}{}{That's more like it. I'll be right back.}
{4020}{}{Changed my mind. Forget it, get your own gun.}
{5000}{}{You're back. Did you get it?}
{5010}{}{Not yet. Where did you say it was again?}
{5020}{}{Sure, here it is.}
{5030}{}{No, sorry, I'll get right on it.}
{6000}{}{My house, south side of town. It's in a footlocker. Learn to pay attention, jeez.}
