{6020}{}{Alright, I'll go get it.}
{7000}{}{Thanks buddy, you're a lifesaver. Hey, keep the ammo. Anything I can do for you?}
{7010}{}{Well, actually, I was thinking of heading out into the wasteland. You got any advice for me?}
{8000}{}{You're fuckin' kidding me. There's a reason we keep to ourselves down here. That place is dangerous.}
{8010}{}{I don't care. I'm going.}
{8020}{}{Don't worry, I can handle myself.}
{9000}{}{You're really thinking about doing this, ain't ya? Aw, hell, not my job to try and stop ya. If you're that set on going, talk to McMurray. He's done a hell of a lot of travelling, he can give you a few pointers.}
{9010}{}{You ever been into the wasteland?}
{9020}{}{Thanks. Take care of yourself, Hull.}
{10000}{}{Well, uh, no. I was born here, and I'm smart enough to know when I got a good thing going.}
{10010}{}{I guess you are. See ya when I see ya.}
{11000}{}{Goddamn it! This ain't right. Wait here a second. Hold my gun. [Hull bolts in the direction of his house, and eventually comes back holding a few handguns] Take one with you. I ain't takin' no for an answer.}
{11010}{}{Uh, okay. What are they?}
{11020}{}{Aw, Hull, you shouldn't have...}
{12000}{}{I got an old Jan-u-wine antique laser pistol, a pretty hefty grenade pistol, and a 10mm semi-automatic.}
{12010}{}{I'm always had a knack for energy weapons. Give me the laser pistol.}
{12020}{}{I like the big guns, give me the grenade launcher.}
{12030}{}{I like to pick 'em off from a distance. Give me the 10mm.}
{13000}{}{You're welcome to it. I'm not sending anyone out into that mess unarmed. Anyone moves funny, you put 'em under the ground, y'hear?}
{13010}{}{Got it. Thanks again, Hull. Goodbye. Take care of yourself.}
